name: Dinosaur Card
description:
These little dinosaurs are very sweet and with a sparkly head, back and tail they are very eye catching.

The dino's come in many colours - so just note which colour you would like. Orange and red, green mix, purple and pink, metalic Bronzes. If no colour is mentioned I send out the green as default.


Hand painted though my hand cut stencils.. you really get a sense of a true handmade cards with these. That said, they are of very high quality!


Card Size: C6 113 x 162mm
Card weight: 300 gsm
Card colour: Light Cream

Card comes with a white envelope and packed in a protective plastic sleeve.
